# Accessibility foundations

Baseline a11y commitments for this product. Concrete, non-negotiable.

## Target standard

- **Conformance:** {{WCAG_2.1_AA_/_WCAG_2.2_AA_/_...}}
- **Audit cadence:** {{every_release_/_quarterly_/_...}}

## Non-negotiables

- Color contrast ≥ 4.5:1 for body text, ≥ 3:1 for large text (WCAG AA)
- All interactive elements keyboard-operable with visible focus
- ARIA labels on icon-only buttons
- Error states announced to screen readers (not just colored red)
- Tap targets ≥ 44×44pt on touch devices

